snippet.title: Knights and Merchants: Remake - changes in upcoming version (r13500+)
snippet.description:
This video sums up new features and improvements added in next new version of KaM Remake, which will hopefully be released soon.


Join KaM Remake official Discord channel, where you can download the beta version already (for testing): https://discord.gg/krCPZ74


Special thanks to Rey, Toxic and everyone else involved in development of this version!
